http://d8rules.org/content/overview-rules-8x-features</p>
<p>Porting Rules to Drupal 8 will require a major refactoring of the framework. The Rules Core APIs &amp; functionality will evolve and Drupal 8 rewrite opportunities will be taken into account.</p>
